ition.\",\n  \"Strategy 4: Move \\\"Review Respondent Bank rating\\\" before the annual-report parallel block and place its rejection handling directly after it. After \\\"obtain respondent bank annual report\\\", execute \\\"Review Respondent Bank rating\\\", then an exclusive node: if data.respondent_bank_rating == \\\"rejected\\\", execute \\\"handle rejection\\\" and \\\"terminate\\\"; otherwise continue to the existing parallel analysis block, with the old rating-review branch removed from that parallel block. This is more intrusive because it changes the parallelization, but it gives the strongest guarantee that rejection immediately leads to termination while preserving the required annual-report activities in the process tree.\"\n]",
